lead_paragraph: The fate of Sunday's intriguing European Championship final between France and Portugal weighs largely on two men wearing the number seven shirt, one already at the top of the game and the other one getting there fast.

headline.print_headline: France Count on Lucky Seven to Spoil Ronaldo Show
